 # Collections & LINQ Patterns

 ### Use FrozenDictionary/FrozenSet for Read-Heavy Lookup Tables
 đźźˇ **DO** use `FrozenDictionary`/`FrozenSet` for collections created once and read many times | .NET 8+

 âťŚ
 ```csharp
