- âś… `[GeneratedRegex]` used with `#if NET7_0_OR_GREATER` â€” source-gen regex on modern TFMs
- âś… Fallback uses `RegexOptions.Compiled` with `static readonly` â€” correct for downlevel
- âś… `Concat(char, ReadOnlySpan<char>)` uses `stackalloc` â€” zero-alloc helper
